high_descs: turn around and cross the room to the counter to the left of the stove
take the knife from the counter
turn around and cross the room to the refrigerator
open the door, slice the apple in the refrigerator, and then close the door
turn around and cross the room to the corner of the counter to the right of the dishwasher
place the knife on the counter
turn around and cross the room to the refrigerator
take an apple wedge from the refrigerator, closing the door afterward
turn around and cross the room to the stove. Stop and look up at the microwave
Place the apple wedge in the microwave, on the right side.  Use the microwave for 5 seconds, then remove the apple.
turn around and cross the room to the corner of the counter by the dishwasher
place the apple wedge to the right of the knife and in front of the spatula
anns.task_desc: Place a warm apple wedge on the counter near the dishwasher

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the counter by the stove.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn around then face the fridge to your right.
Open the fridge, slice the apple inside then close the fridge.
Turn around and head to the counter in front of you.
Place the knife on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the fridge in front of you.
Open the fridge in front of you, take an apple slice out and close the fridge.
Turn right and face the microwave on top of the stove.
Heat up the apple slice in the microwave in front of you and take out the apple slice.
Turn around and face the counter on your left.
Place the apple slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot apple slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the fridge, go forward to the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge into pieces.
Turn around, go forward to the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Take a piece of apple from the fridge.
Turn around, go forward, turn left to the oven, go forward to the oven.
Cook the apple in the microwave above the oven. Take the apple from the oven.
Turn around, go forward, turn left to the counter to the right of the dishwasher, go forward to the counter.
Put the apple in front of the spatula near the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the left and walk over to the black cabinet.
Open the cabinet and cut the apple in the cabinet into 3 pieces.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the cabinet.
Pick up a piece of apple from the cabinet.
Turn to the right and walk over to the stove.
Heat the apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around walk across the room and then face the counter on the left.
Put the apple slice on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife plus an apple slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter that is left of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Cut the apple into sections.
Turn right, move to the counter that is right of the dishwasher.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Pick up a section of apple from the refrigerator.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Place the apple section into the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter that is right of the dishwasher.
Place the apple section onto the counter, right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked section of apple onto the counter.
